item.title: By: ListlessSpectre
item.dc:creator: ListlessSpectre
item.description: I have to compliment Afro Thunder on this one. I get hints of what seems like sugar cookie, graham cracker, chocolate and some toasted almond and it's da bomb! It's not overly sweet and very mellow. I've been through tank after tank with complete satisfaction. Definitely an ADV for anyone looking for a tasty treat!
